message.body: Did you grab the electrical bag by chance?
Can I come get it now?
I'll have all your stuff back to you Wednesday if that's cool.
Could I use yr basement for a half hour tonight? I need to rip a few things that the portable table saw is too small for.
Actually can I use the basement tomorrow morning instead?
I still have piles of cedar everywhere that I need to organize or get rid of, but I guess u can. Got class, no more correspondence from me for the night
No worries. I'm can work in James' shop.
